%N A397758 Decimal expansion of Sum_{k>=1} (zeta(3) - H(k,3))*H(k)/(k+1), where H(k) = A001008(k)/A002805(k) is the k-th harmonic number, and H(k,3) = A007408(k)/A007409(k) is the k-th generalized harmonic number of order 3.
